				class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current"
			>
				<path
					stroke-linecap="round"
					stroke-linejoin="round"
					stroke-width="2"
					d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
				></path>
			</svg>
			<span>Some skills that you see here might not be in the game yet. Make sure to refresh this page before doing any modification to get latest changes from the server.</span>
